data.description: Wisconsin riverfront home on Merrill’s Westside! This riverfront home offers incredible views of the Wisconsin River right out your back door. Cozy main entrance to the home opens to the main level. Open concept design with two bedrooms on the main level with ample space. Owners suite features two closets and in addition, wonderful views of the river. Spacious full main level bathroom with large counter/vanity space. Kitchen opens to dinette area and has lots of cabinets as well as all the kitchen appliances. The large living room area offers stunning window views of the River as well as new patio door to the covered backyard deck! New vinyl/laminate flooring throughout the main level and lots of natural light throughout the home. Lower level home boasts a sizeable family room with brand new carpet installed. There is an electric stone fireplace with lots of character and mini bar area.
